title: How To: Make Flat Bread Sticks With Miele Appliances
description:
Miele Appliance Training:

Flat Bread Sticks:

The Miele Moisture plus feature provides a flakier consistency.

Ingredients:
- 1 tsp chopped fresh thyme
- 1 tsp chopped fresh rosemary
- 1 tsp chopped fresh oregano
- 1 rolle Pillsbury pizza dough
- 2 Tbsp shredded parmesan cheese
- Sea salt
- Fresh Cracked black pepper
- 1 Stick Butter
- 1 Tbsp chopped garlic

Directions:
1. Preheat oven to Moisture Plus; Convection Bake: 400F
2. Roll out pizza dough
3. Place on perforated baking tray
4. Brush with garlic butter
5. Sprinkle with herbs salt pepper and parmesan
6. Slice into 8-10 even strips
7. Place in oven Level 2
8. 1 burst of steam bake until golden 8-12 minutes
